    dc:description "FIGURES 274, 275. Chrysoctonus sp., habitus. USA, Florida, Alachua Co., Gainesville, AEI, 29°35'53\"N 82°21'54\"W, 8– 25.x.2003, D.B. Wahl. 274, female; 275, male. Scale bars=500 μm." ;
